data.description: Fully furnished 4 bedroom 3 bath vacation resort luxury town home in the very desirable resort community of Regal Palms. This home has everything you need to really start enjoying your weekends like you deserve or perhaps you want to invest in a short term vacation rental that can produce you income.Regal Palms is a private, gated resort  and it is just 15 minutes from the Disney Theme Parks.The resort has a large tropical pool with lazy river, water slide, waterfalls, and jacuzzi. Just some of the amenities include fitness center and sauna are all available for the exclusive use of guests & owners.
